WEBVTT

00:02:29.287 --> 00:02:31.260
"Double" so'zining ma'nosi,

00:02:31.260 --> 00:02:32.133
ikki,

00:02:32.133 --> 00:02:35.778
"doubt" so'zining tubida yotadi.

00:02:35.778 --> 00:02:37.319
Biz shubhalanganimizda,

00:02:37.319 --> 00:02:38.831
ikkilanganimizda,

00:02:38.831 --> 00:02:41.497
biz o'zimizga bashorat qilamiz.

00:02:41.497 --> 00:02:43.675
Bizda nimadandir shubha bo'lsa,

00:02:43.675 --> 00:02:46.129
bizda savollar ko'p bo'lganida yoki 
adashganimizda

00:02:46.129 --> 00:02:48.876
biz qat'iyatsiz bo'lamiz.

00:02:48.876 --> 00:02:51.544
Tarixan,
ingliz tili fransuz tilidan

00:02:51.544 --> 00:02:53.234
so'zlar kirita boshlaganida,

00:02:53.234 --> 00:02:55.506
shubha degan so'z allaqachon 
mavjud bo'lgan.

00:02:55.506 --> 00:02:59.152
U eski inglizcha so'z "tweogan" edi.

00:02:59.152 --> 00:03:01.585
